WEBVTT

00:01:28.882 --> 00:01:30.221
that's me.

00:01:30.245 --> 00:01:31.293
(Laughter)

00:01:31.317 --> 00:01:32.763
And I'm going to tell you why,

00:01:32.787 --> 00:01:35.109
but first, let me tell you
how we got started.

00:01:35.863 --> 00:01:37.013
So a lot of people ask,

00:01:37.037 --> 00:01:38.471
"How did Rco come to be?"

00:01:38.495 --> 00:01:40.033
And I have to be really honest.

00:01:40.419 --> 00:01:42.424
I leveraged my white privilege.

00:01:42.764 --> 00:01:46.417
So, here's how white privilege
worked for me and Rco.

00:01:47.448 --> 00:01:51.293
My white grandmother
was born on her family's plantation

00:01:51.317 --> 00:01:53.971
in Arkansas in 1918.

00:01:53.995 --> 00:01:56.925
She traveled with her white father west,

00:01:56.949 --> 00:01:58.518
following the oil boom.

